snippet.textDisplay: Also why is there no Indian version of this song? By "Indian version" I meant a complete setup of only "Indian" instruments.  The sound of those instruments would compliment the rugged vocal style of Vishal and lyrics as well and it'd also bring out the true flavour of this song. Anyway, the "Wah" effect of the Dunlop Crybaby effects pedal at 3:45 is nice.
